  "detailed_description": "These Nights Alone is a point-and-click mystery novel with multiple endings.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1468000/extras/dccb81f5bc976997e19591e4241bdae9.webp?t=1667063248\" width=66 height=38 /></span><br><br>Alice is a young woman who recently lost her husband, James, in a car accident. <br>Right before the accident, James wanted to talk to her about something very important.<br>All alone in their new house, she decides to investigate. <br><br>What is she going to discover? How the story will end? Who is lying to her?<br><br><strong>The evolution of the story depends on your choices. </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1468000/extras/b53b16a2355f85dff7430f3b364e2d0d.webp?t=1667063248\" width=283 height=62 /></span>",
